00:33:41,800 --> 00:33:42,880
Take me away from here.

497
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:46,870
♪The wind whispers of the past, how can sorrow be told?♪

498
00:33:46,870 --> 00:33:50,740
♪When the long night paints your silhouette♪

