00:34:21,910 --> 00:34:24,690
♪Love begins like a shackle♪

505
00:34:25,300 --> 00:34:28,550
♪Fate parts ways and drifts afar♪

506
00:34:29,910 --> 00:34:32,520
♪In a moment of longing, it falls apart♪

507
00:34:33,140 --> 00:34:36,160
♪Tears surge into a whirlpool♪

508
00:34:37,090 --> 00:34:39,600
♪The tangled karma♪

509
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:44,580
♪Cannot bloom the flowers of togetherness♪

510
00:34:44,900 --> 00:34:49,150
♪Where is the moonlight to answer our vows♪

511
00:34:49,160 --> 00:34:52,960
♪And to shine upon you and me♪

512
00:34:54,370 --> 00:34:58,330
♪Gathering and parting, how can sorrow be told?♪

513
00:34:58,330 --> 00:35:02,310
♪When will love's silk be woven into brocade?♪

514
00:35:03,920 --> 00:35:05,360
I can't go home.

515
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:10,170
♪May my deepest affection last forever, like clouds with starlight♪

516
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:11,040
Alright.

517
00:35:11,040 --> 00:35:19,380
♪Who will hold my hand, bound by life and death?♪

518
00:35:58,600 --> 00:35:59,400
Yang Jinglan.

519
00:36:01,160 --> 00:36:01,960
I'm here.

520
00:36:03,560 --> 00:36:04,400
I'm hungry.

521
00:36:06,800 --> 00:36:09,040
Alright, I'll go get you something to eat.

522
00:36:09,560 --> 00:36:10,720
Wait here for me.

523
00:37:36,560 --> 00:37:37,840
Dear, no need to look.

524
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:39,000
I've already

525
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:40,800
sent your people away.

526
00:37:49,880 --> 00:37:51,160
Today is a day of great joy.

527
00:37:51,520 --> 00:37:53,520
Why do you look so unhappy?

528
00:37:58,000 --> 00:37:58,800
What's wrong?

529
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:01,040
After you've done so much for her,

530
00:38:01,640 --> 00:38:03,160
she still won't accept you?

531
00:38:13,200 --> 00:38:16,240
I'm already in such a sorry state,

532
00:38:17,120 --> 00:38:18,920
why should I care about the rain?

533
00:38:22,960 --> 00:38:24,440
In my father's eyes,

534
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:26,360
