541
00:38:45,840 --> 00:38:47,080
We're tragic lovers.

542
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:51,640
After going through so much,

543
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:54,520
I realized

544
00:38:55,800 --> 00:38:57,680
the only one left by my side in the end

545
00:38:58,760 --> 00:39:00,080
is you.

546
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:07,560
Sir,

547
00:39:07,760 --> 00:39:08,880
General Niu's men are here.

548
00:39:10,200 --> 00:39:11,960
Mr. Zhao, the General wants to see you.

549
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:13,240
Come with me to the barracks.

550
00:39:16,080 --> 00:39:16,880
Dear,

551
00:39:17,560 --> 00:39:18,960
I'll change into some new clothes.

552
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:39,920
My father only wants to see him?

553
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:40,880
Madam,

554
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:42,960
the General only mentioned Mr. Zhao.

555
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:44,000
