581
00:40:54,440 --> 00:40:55,240
So,

582
00:40:56,560 --> 00:40:59,160
the only way to keep him loyal to us

583
00:41:00,520 --> 00:41:02,040
is to make him stay silent forever.

584
00:41:12,240 --> 00:41:13,280
Stand up.

585
00:41:23,440 --> 00:41:26,200
